snippet.title: Newton | Launch Trailer | Out Now!
snippet.description:
Newton is completely FREE! Jump off the page and defy gravity itself: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3419790/Newton/

Newton is a simple 2D pixel art platformer. Collect apples, master gravity and set high scores in this simple but challenging adventure!
